    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "but i really dont want to go to the doctor right now, it's so expensive and i'm pretty sure it's just from the screen time. if i just use the lubricating drops maybe it'll soothe the irritation enough that it goes away on its own? it doesn't feel *that* bad, just uncomfortable. like, is it really that urgent to go see someone immediately?",
