    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "i guess. it's just a hassle. if i do use the drops, is there anything else i can do at home to speed it up so i don't have to go? like maybe a warm compress or some kind of antibiotic ointment i might have in my first aid kit? i'm really hoping to just handle this myself tonight.",
